                        <h1>How we do things</h1>
                        <p>Ruckus Peak sources adult outwear in need of a touch of TLC from second hand retailers and sellers in order to revive the items to produce quality clothing for an affordable budget. All products are sourced locally, handpicked by ourselves and acquired in the most efficient and environmentally responsible way possible.</p>
